<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6500903>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Holotype of Hemidactylus srikanthani sp. nov. (in life) from Devarayana Durga Hills, Tumkur District, Karnataka, India." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6500903/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6500905>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Preserved holotype of Hemidactylus srikanthani sp. nov. (BNHS 2640)—A. dorsal view of entire specimen; B. ventral view of entire specimen; C. right side of the head; D. left side of the head; E. ventral view of the head; F. dorsal view of the head; G. lamellae on right manus; H. lamellae on right pes; I. precloacal-femoral pores. [Scale bar: A. & B.: 10 mm; C., D., E. & F.: 5 mm; G. & H.: 2 mm]" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6500905/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6500901>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Habitat at the type locality of Hemidactylus mahonyi sp. nov. Sandur (Joga village), Bellary District, Karnataka, India." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6500901/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6500907>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Preserved paratype of Hemidactylus srikanthani sp. nov. (BNHS 2641)—A. dorsal view of entire specimen; B. ventral view of entire specimen. [Scale bar: A. & B.: 10 mm.]" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6500907/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6500889>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Map of southern India depicting the type localities of the two new species—black circle (Sandur Hills):Hemidactylus mahonyi sp. nov. and red circle (Devarayana Durga Hills): Hemidactylus srikanthani sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6500889/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6500909>
    dc:description "FIGURE 10. Habitat at the type locality of Hemidactylus srikanthani sp. nov. Devarayana Durga Hills, Tumkur District, Karnataka, India" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6500909/files/figure.png" ;
